reviews.review: Good story for the ending of the series that answers lots of questions asked over the years!
Good movie. Would recommend. Great to see the Emperor again.
JJ did all he could with the mess Rian left behind.
This movie is the final nail in the star wars coffin.  Far tip many plot holes.

I really wanted to dislike this movie. I hated what they did to Luke in the last Jedi. After hearing about the return of Palpatine, I was worried they ruined Vader's legacy as well. 

I was wrong. This is an exciting adventure from beginning to end. No I am not a bot or paid off reviewer, just a big Star Wars since fan 1980.

What made the movie for me was Ben Solo. He finally became a Jedi at the end of the movie, and redeemed himself, just like his Grand father.

I'd recommend this movie.
It was the best movie of the new trilogy, sadly that is not saying much. The story started off terrible so their wasnt much this movie really could have done to fix it.

Entertaining, exciting, shocking and as much fun as a Star Wars movie should be. They did an awesome job of tying up some loose ends, throwing in a few easter eggs and fan surprises and it ended where it all began, as it should.

This Movie was really good i enjoyed it in 3D. If you listen to the reviews here you would think you went to a different film. First its called scifi,second its a finaly to along franchise.it could not be a film, 4 to 5 hours long to recap and re invent all preceding 
Films that came before it.if you don't see the other films then you miss alot of interplay this movie accomplishes. Both with the films from before and the new releases.it's a satisfying conclusion and an openning to the next chapter of the Starwars SciFi saga.it has a little bit of everything you could want in an enjoyable
Movie. My advice dont listen to the critics or the YouTube's if you like starwars see  see it in 3D its worth it
Fine movie that could be watched although would be confusing having not seen the previous movies.
Everything was rushed and disjointed. Some of the dialogue even seemed to be spoken quickly in order to get to the next scene
